{"word":"μείων","slug":"μείων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μείων</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>irr. <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> of <a href='S:μικρός'><el>μικρός</el></a>\n<p/><i>less</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: <i>older</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <el>μεῖον</el>, as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <i>less</i>, <el>μ. ἰσχύσειν Διός</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:— <el>μειόνως ἔχειν</el> to be <i>of less value</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}